Insider Activity


Individual




Seth H. Bagshaw



Mr. Seth H. Bagshaw is President & Director at Newport Corp. and CFO, Treasurer, VP & Head-Investor Relations at MKS Instruments, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Newport Corp., Associated Industries of Massachusetts, and Vamosa Ltd.
Mr. Bagshaw was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Vice President by Vette Corp., Vice President & Controller by Varian Semiconductor Equipment Associates, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Vice President by Palo Alto Products International Ltd, Chief Financial Officer-Asia Pacific Region by Waters Corp., and Senior Manager by Pricewaterhousecoopers LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from Boston University and an MBA from Cornell University.



